name: Seed Bearing Herb
description:
All is one. There is only one being... You. Everything is you in one form or another. Doing unto others as we would have them do unto us extends beyond humans. Treat all life with the compassion you'd want, if the roles were reversed. The greater one is a conglomeration of all the parts of one. 

The text in this art is from the Akashic Records; it's the original intended translation from spirit. We know Genesis 1:30 is a gross mistranslation because other animals cannot read, and therefore do not need a line in a book transcribed to them.
